&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=rxin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;rxin&quot;&gt;rxin&lt;/a&gt; is this a bug or actually intended behavior (and I&apos;m just not interpreting correctly)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14721302" author="apachespark" created="Sat, 29 Aug 2015 23:59:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User &apos;feynmanliang&apos; has created a pull request for this issue:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8523&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/spark/pull/8523&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14721318" author="rxin" created="Sun, 30 Aug 2015 00:42:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;getString is only used in debugging I think?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14721325" author="fliang" created="Sun, 30 Aug 2015 00:54:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sorry, the fix is for &lt;tt&gt;getUTF8String&lt;/tt&gt;. &lt;tt&gt;getString&lt;/tt&gt; is the method which causes the &lt;tt&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/tt&gt;. Updated title.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
